David Cameron has revealed he and his wife Samantha were 'falling apart'
He said the stress of looking after their son Ivan pushed their relationship close to 'breaking point'
The Prime Minister said Ivan was a 'blessing in lots of ways' but admitted the strain of trying to care for him left them 'totally shattered'
Ivan was born with Ohtahara Syndrome, a rare brain disorder which left him needing round-the-clock care .